  "title": "Purchaser",
  "description": "<p>Conducting research on potential products, vendors, and services, and comparing price and quality to ensure the best deal. </p>\n<p>· Liaising with delivery and warehouse teams to ensure goods are received on time. · Inspective purchased products upon delivery. · Writing reports on purchases made and performing cost analysis. · Planning and prioritizing operations to ensure maximum performance and minimum delay. .Update purchase records accordingly. Requirements · Strong analytical skills · Good written, verbal, and interpersonal skills · Practical experience with purchasing. · Excellent knowledge of production planning and quality control principles · Good at math and statistics · Strong organizational and problem-solving skills · Excellent communication abilities</p>",
