    "uen": "199802637G",
    "description": "<p><strong>Accesstech</strong> is a rapidly expanding group of companies with interest in <strong>Engineering Construction</strong>, <strong>Telecommunications</strong> and <strong>Investments</strong>. Founded in 1998 in Singapore with our principal business in high-tech factory engineering, we have since extended our expertise into commercial projects with luxury hotels and commercial properties. <strong>Quality</strong>, <strong>Educations</strong> and <strong>Environmental Health</strong> and <strong>Safety</strong> are foremost values in the company. <strong>Accesstech </strong>is <strong>ISO 9001</strong>, <strong>ISO 14000</strong> and <strong>OHSAS 18001</strong> certified. Our <strong>Integrated Management Systems</strong> promised the simplicity of delivery and assurance of our performance. <strong>Click here</strong> to find out more.</p>    <p><strong>PEOPLE </strong>are the basis of a company potential. The fundamental success of a company will very much rely on its team of workforce. The company now seeks to secure further mid-and senior level leadership and functional support positions. We are seeking independent individuals who have the passion and drive to join our growing family.</p>    <p>Remuneration will commensurate with your education level and working experience. We invite you to send in your CV (cover letter with a detailed resume) in MS Word format and email us at <strong>c</strong><strong>areer@accesstech.com.sg</strong> stating the job function in the email title.</p>    <p>Please include your current and expected salary and your availability in your CV for us to conduct a more effective job matching. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. All applications will be held in strict confidence.</p>  ",
